{
  "stem": "10710.3",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I didn't know anybody.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So I was, you know, I was not from Krakow, from the group.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I was just there from-- but there was one man that he knew me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He owned the factory of of-- where Schindler took over the factory.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "His name was Abraham Banker.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "He took over the factory from Schindler-- from-- Schindler took over the factory from him.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And he-- he was a religious man, that Banker, before the war.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And in camp, he tried to keep as much as you could.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And he knew a little bit about me, that I was in camp, and I was-- I used to daven.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "He shown me once, we had not film, but we-- sometimes we borrowed film.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We used to daven.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And they were calling people, like a thousand people, and it-- I was left with few people already.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Because whoever called in went down to the group there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And then they called my name, too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I was almost maybe five of the list want to be called.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "It's like, you know, like a new-- new way of life.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "You get a new certificate of life if you heard your name being called.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I knew I'm going with Schindler, and I knew I'm going to be protected, because he wanted to save the people.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was his-- his aim, to save the people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know what people talk-- what he did, but he was an angel.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He must have been sent from God.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because how could he-- he was-- he was an SS man before.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He joined the party.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But then he saw what the Germans were doing to the Jews.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He had a change-- change of-- of thinking, what they do to them.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
